nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE PASSING EAST OF BERMUDA... ...INTERESTS IN THE AZORES SHOULD MONITOR ITS PROGRESS...
summary: ...GABRIELLE PASSING EAST OF BERMUDA... ...INTERESTS IN THE AZORES SHOULD MONITOR ITS PROGRESS... As of 11:00 PM AST Mon Sep 22 the center of Gabrielle was located near 32.4, -61.0 with movement NE at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 948 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 140 mph.
